Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:32.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}这句话已听过无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:38.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}即便装作没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:45.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}也并无区别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:52.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我知道 是你教给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:02:00.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}就算失败 也并不代表做不到
